results.title: Live, laugh, love - sticker - laptop decal - mirror decal - window decal - car decal
results.description:
Live, laugh, love decal. Made from high quality outdoor vinyl adhesive, this is the perfect decal for yourself or a great gift for friends and family members.

***Please note due to different computer screen settings colors may differ slightly***

These decals are removable, but not reusable. They can be applied to any clean, smooth/semi-smooth surface. For example- laptops, phones, tablets, cars and car windows, refrigerators, mugs, water bottles, wine glasses, lockers, mirrors, windows, and many more! Do not use in the dishwasher, always hand wash items you choose to put them on when needed.

It is highly recommended that you do not put this type of decal on painted walls as they might cause damage when removing. If you would like something to put on your walls, we will be doing wall decals soon, contact us if you're interested.


NOTE: Size reference in photos are for viewing purposes only and may not reflect the actual size of the decal.

100% Made in the USA

They are waterproof, weatherproof, and will not fade or crack in the sun. They can last up to six years outdoors and ten years indoors.

 

                                      Directions

 1. Clean surface well before application, rubbing alcohol works best.

2. Allow surface to dry.

3. Carefully peel backing away from decal at the top edge.

4. Apply top edge of decal to surface.

5. Carefully continue to peel backing down, smoothing the decal into place using even firm pressure.

6. Carefully remove clear protective film.

results.title: Live Love Laugh necklace, Affirmation necklace gift, Positive affirmation jewelry, 14K gold filled, sterling silver
results.description:
Live Love Laugh necklace, Affirmation necklace gift, Positive affirmation jewelry, 14K gold-filled, sterling silver

Let this classic interlocking circles necklace be a positive reminder of three words to live by! A thoughtful and meaningful symbolistic piece that will allow you to keep this mantra close to your heart. A present that will be treasured for many years to come. 14K gold-filled and sterling silver rings are soldered in our studio and hand textured with a tiny hammer to create one of a kind pendant. 

- ALL components are made with precious metals, 14K Gold Filled & Sterling silver. We never use cheaply plated, quick to tarnish materials - that is our promise. 

- Necklace is 18” long with adjustable hook at 16”. To request a custom length, please leave us a message at checkout. 

- Beautifully packaged in our custom designed jewelry box with a blank greeting card, a thoughtful message, a jewelry care guide and a polish cloth. 

- We are happy to write a note on the greeting card, just leave us a message at checkout.

About 14K Gold Filled: 

Gold filled jewelry contains a thick layer of real gold. It is a durable, long-lasting precious metal with the prettiest light gold tone. To create gold filled jewelry, multiple layers of solid gold are pressure-bonded to a core of high-quality jeweler’s brass using extreme heat. Gold filled metals are at least 15 times more expensive than plated gold materials. Unlike gold plated metals, gold filled metal price depends on the market value of gold at the time of purchase.

Will Gold Filled ever tarnish?
Gold fill can tarnish naturally over time, but it’s easily cleaned. We include a polish cloth in our packaging which we recommend using only when your piece is dull or tarnished—not for everyday cleaning purposes. It should be used LIGHTLY and not pressed hard against the metal to remove tarnish, as it could rub off the gold on your piece over time.
